@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
autonumber

title US-04 Input Parameters (Current Code Reality)

actor Developer
participant "Encoder Constructors" as EC
participant "InputHandler" as IH
participant "Agent" as AG

Developer -> EC: pass encoder parameters\n(e.g., ScalarEncoderParameters, RDSEParameters)
EC --> Developer: configured encoder instances

Developer -> IH: input_data(..., required_columns)
activate IH
IH -> IH: _apply_required_columns(required_columns)
IH --> Developer: normalized records
deactivate IH

Developer -> AG: create_pooler(...)/create_memory(...)
activate AG
AG --> Developer: components appended
deactivate AG

note over Developer,AG
No GlobalOptimizer/ParameterOptimizer class exists.
Parameter tuning is manual via constructor args.
end note
@enduml
